Subject: clk: qcom: gcc-ipq9574: add WCSS Q6 clocks

Expose the IPQ9574 GCC branch clocks required to start the WCSS Q6
remote processor. The native WCSS loader needs a pre-boot clock set and
a smaller post-boot clock set before ath11k can obtain its remoteproc.

Signed-off-by: Alexandru Gagniuc <mr.nuke.me@gmail.com>
Signed-off-by: Igor Kravchenko <igor.kravchenko05@gmail.com>
